name: Going to GOD | Break of 2021 (Community)
description:
Going to GOD

2021 means that a terrible epidemic covid-19 corona's terrible grip is floating in front of us. All around, students, workers, professional employees, or businessmen are all under house arrest. Their income decreases so a wail begins to be found all around; The burning smell of death echoed across the sky. School and college are still closed in Bangladesh!

Anxious students and adults continue to pray to God for help.


#wowrakibul
